rules.name: myRule_14
rules.label: Contact owner same as Account owner

value.stringValue:

OR( [Contact].Account.Sales_Org__r.Sales_Org_Code__c = $Label.NAM_SalesOrg, [Contact].Account.Sales_Org__r.Sales_Org_Code__c = $Label.Canada_SalesOrg ), OR( ISCHANGED([Contact].County__c ), ISCHANGED([Contact].Street__c ), ISCHANGED([Contact].ZIP_Code__c ), ISCHANGED([Contact].US_State__c), ISCHANGED([Contact].City__c ), ISNEW() ) )
